data.oai_dc:dc: Mammals of Big Sur: Literature Survey

Gives behavioral and life history information regarding several species of mammals that live in Big Sur. Organized by order-family-genus-species-and common name. The report is laid out in three parts looking at terrestrial and some marine mammals and effects of 1)different biomes such as grassland, woodland, and chaparral, 2) vegetation and 3)climate, on wildlife use.
